Scott Alomes



Mr. Scott Alomes is Chief Human Resources Officer at EZCORP, Inc. and a Member at Australian Human Resources Institute.
Mr. Alomes was previously employed as Head-Marketing & Human Resources by ClearView Wealth Ltd., Senior Executive-Human Resources by Suncorp-Metway Ltd., Executive General Manager by Commonwealth Bank of Australia, and General Manager-People & Culture by National Australia Bank Ltd.



